body.pre: Model of the yeast cell cycle originally described in Oguz et al (2013) "Optimization and model reduction in the high dimensional parameter space of a budding yeast cell cycle model" BMC Syst. Biol. Adapted to SBML format and used as an example problem in Mitra et al (2018) "Using both qualitative and quantitative data to imporve parameter identification for systems biology models".
